Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.71,0:00:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He has already gone to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.25,0:00:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All that remains here is\NRichard Braun's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,His soul will live on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us swear on his soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that we will continue on living... in hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us turn to the Bible, Psalm 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is quite unbearable, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What a depressing funeral...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he was a skilled detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,not a single person from the\Npolice department came.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,While he was part of the force,\Nhe had a drinking problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, he drank and fell to his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the police said, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,On the day he died,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard had apparently promised his\Ndaughter to see her the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I ever do for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Reichwein...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I just sat in my chair,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,listened to his story,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and told him that he had regained his old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I ever do for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could find him, it's possible\Nthat everything would be solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.09,0:01:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's strange, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.67,0:01:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This was no accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This was not a suicide either!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Richard spoke to his daughter on the\Nphone just a few hours before his death,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.35,0:01:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,saying they'd meet the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you did everything that you could have done,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and Mr. Richard did regain his old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:02:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't blame yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:38.04,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\pos(360,340)}Decision
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me out, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband will not talk to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since I found out about his affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day, he washes the car and\Nthen mows the lawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't even look me in the face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:04:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's better than his not coming home,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but if this continues, I think I'll go crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I stormed over to his mistress's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and what do you think happened then, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The possibility of a homicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That night, Richard Braun went up to the the roof\Nof Building 12 at the University of Munich,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,drank a bottle of whiskey, and then\Nfell off after getting drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you investigate the bottle closely?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard's fingerprints were on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you show me that bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Richard spoke to his daughter on the\Nphone just a few hours before his death,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,saying they'd meet the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,this person came here that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He came alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So you remember his coming here, but you don't\Nremember if he came with someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I remembered him because\Nhe ordered coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unusual for a customer to come in that\Nlate at night and not order alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That night,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,was he with this young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of customers come in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true that he bought a\Nbottle of whiskey to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right there on the receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it really Richard who bought it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I don't remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The receipt only has "one bottle of Racke" on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One bottle of Racke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I realize it when I saw the\Nbottle label at the police station?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:06:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You drank again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you have to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whiskey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I only drink whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Stinking up the room\Nwith the smell of Racke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Racke?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never drink that domestic stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When I drink I drink the\Nreal stuff, Scotch Whiskey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a given!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who bought the\Nwhiskey was not Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Johann...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it him, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:07:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:07:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you try to push me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You got some business with my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who hired you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about your age, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A grandpa should just look after his grandkids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, you punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've trained with the border patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you try to push me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate a former police surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I was hired to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A big man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A big man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A big man that I passed in the subway\Npassage gave me money!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me to push you off...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it for you, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's real Scotch Whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to drink it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink all you want now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,leave it to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely figure it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,His...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Johann's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,real identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, doctor, I told my husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your infidelity is like a disease,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and, "You're the only one who should\Nbe getting a doctor's counseling!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course, Mrs. Hesse...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If my husband stays that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,my depression will get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not really suffering\Nfrom depression, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more worried about your quiet husband, who\Nwashes his car and mows the lawn every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird, no matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm free the day after tomorrow at 5 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try asking my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please straighten out that cheating oaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you have no more patients today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. That's all for today, Ms. Merez.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave first, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ms. Merez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, you forgot to lock\Nthe back door again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was about to forget today, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, is this Dr. Gillen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I read the newspaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that ad that you put out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's discuss our memories of\Ncheating. From Rudi."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Dr. Tenma really contact you\Nbecause of this one sentence?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If Tenma sees that, he will\Ndefinitely contact me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a story that only\Nthe two of us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, please don't do anything\Nrash until he appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one thing I would like\Nto investigate, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The prostitute named Margot Langer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When Fahren, who committed suicide,\Nwent to see that woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a youth with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful, blonde young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of exposing the truth, I will\Nbe more cautious from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,for Richard's sake as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll contact you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Merez, you forgot to close\Nthe window today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Margot Langer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,her current nickname should be\NSophie something or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that fat hag?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, are you into those types of girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be embarrassed at your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Two streets down, around the corner.\NSecond floor of the old building.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not there now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen her lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She probably found a better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A better... place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, why are the fat ugly ones so popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that a really rich guy came\Nto see her the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! How about me, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can definitely entertain you better\Nthan that fat hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know where she went?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have gone somewhere\Nwith that new guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,New guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can't believe that old hag fell\Nin love with that big man at her age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a big man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A big man...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked like he was big down there, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I take the rest of the day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working until five today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have left is an appointment with\Nthat unfaithful husband, so go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a date, right, Ms. Merez?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please remember the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If I show this photo to that prostitute Sophie,\Nwho pretended to be Margot Langer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and got her to testify that the one who\Nwas with Fahren was this boy, Johann,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be one step closer to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hesse. My wife made an\Nappointment for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll try questioning that\Nwoman again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Mr. Hesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time at a counseling session so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be nervous about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a place where you can relax\Nand tell me anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What you say here is strictly confidential,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,so please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How have you been lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bothering me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She found out about my affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in my own house, I don't feel at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so I mow the lawn and wash the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I do that every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And does that make you feel any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even talk to my wife at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't an opportunity to talk\Neven when you want to, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not sure if that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the woman you\Nhad an affair with?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I dreamt that I'd killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you often have those kinds of dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Often...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... not lately, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you had an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was after I met him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a beautiful boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with blonde hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many people I killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,or even if the country was destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,everything inside of me felt like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,After I met him, though, things changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything began to seem real...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was no longer lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Would...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you wait a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My secretary went home, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, she has a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She makes good tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I can't give you some.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In a job like yours, many different\Nthings must occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you do learn about people's dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good can result from learning about\Ndreams that you shouldn't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,learning that I'm a murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I-In any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,if you intend to start over\Nas husband and wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you should talk things over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope that you didn't close\Nthe back door, Ms. Merez.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor... Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching over you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
